            <h2>Advanced Training Program: Push Your Limits</h2>
            <p>Welcome to the advanced training program designed for those seeking to push their physical limits. This program combines strength, endurance, and advanced techniques. Here's a sample workout routine:</p>

            <h3>Day 1: Strength and Power</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Barbell Squats: 5 sets of 5 reps</li>
                <li>Explosive Push-ups: 4 sets of 10 reps</li>
                <li>Single-Arm Dumbbell Rows: 4 sets of 8 reps per arm</li>
                <li>Plank with Weighted Vest: 4 sets, 45 seconds each</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Day 2: Advanced Cardiovascular Training</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Interval Sprints: 10 sets of 30 seconds sprinting, 30 seconds rest</li>
                <li>Box Jumps with Burpees: 4 sets of 15 reps</li>
                <li>Battle Rope Waves: 3 sets of 1 minute</li>
                <li>Rest: 2 minutes between sets</li>
            </ul>

            <p>This program demands dedication and proper recovery. Ensure proper form during exercises and consider working with a certified fitness professional for guidance.</p>
